  <brief_title>High-dose Chemotherapy and Stem Cell Transplantation for Central Nervous System (CNS) Relapse of Aggressive Lymphomas</brief_title>
  <official_title>Combined Systemic and Intrathecal Chemotherapy Followed by High-dose Chemotherapy and Autologous Stem Cell Transplantation for CNS Relapse of Aggressive Lymphomas</official_title>
